description:
Rogue Cheney (Future) is Rogue Cheney`s future counterpart. He was originally thought to have traveled back in time to kill Lucy Heartfilia, who closed the Eclipse Gate, leaving the world at the mercy of the 10,000 Dragons. However, his true intent lies in his bid to kill Acnologia and become the new Dragon King.
Source: Fairy Tail Wikia
name: Rogue Cheney
